Portable and extendable source code for virtual stack machine
Small runtime with 100+ primitive operations
Should allow extension with additional primitive operations
Fast threading (next, nest, unnest)

Support programming in the large ie modules, packaging and strick versioning
Compile module source to object code and/or implementation language code
Static code coverage and usage profile at compile time
Support code modules and simple dependency definition
Object code file format should allow loading of code only
Archive file with multiple versions of object files
Strip symbol table from object code 

Dynamic or minimum linking of object code at run-time
Relocatable object code (modules)

Build-in support for tracing, profiling and coverage 
Dynamic code coverage and usage profile at runtime time
Run-time switching between tracing, profiling and normal execution
Debugging support should be removable



